{"word":"G3898 - παραπλησίως - paraplēsíōs - par-ap-lay-see'-oce - Likewise","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραπλησίως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paraplēsíōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ap-lay-see'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Likewise</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"போல - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"similarly, in like manner, in the same way"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from the same as <a href=\"#/G3897 - παραπλήσιον - paraplḗsion - par-ap-lay'-see-on/3897\">G3897</a>; <i>in a manner near by</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>similarly:</i> - likewise.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}